channel.title: Development team for the first 602!
channel.description:
Thats correct! you read right! a 602!!
I ask that after reading this thread you visit this topic for the sources base information: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,434284.0.html
I am in need of 2 coders for now more to come later. -Positions left -1: Llaver -2: Still available -3: Still available
Some goals:
A less complicated version of dungeoneering
A few quests
All bosses
Perfect pking
A few minigames
A good economy
Possibly a grand Exchange
I would like to let everyone that is wanting this position that i do not want to own this server completely. I am wanting 2 other coders and I to be co-owning this server and all three will recieve Owner rank. One more thing i would like is that if you would like to join you download skype and find/buy a microphone that plugs into the computer for use of fast easy voice chat.
Development pictures: [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/4g3jtg.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/2z6c7eg.jpg[/img] Sadly my comp is to old to run on hd so none of the good stuff lol
If you would like to be part of this development team just use the template and I will read over it and decide(: [code]Name: Country + Time Zone: Experience + Proof: Skype or MSN:[/code]
Thanks for taking the time to read this and hope you want to join!!
